	<div id="tab1" style="width:100%;float:left;" class="calibri">
      <h2>detached holiday cottage in mid wales with woodburner & wifi</h2>
      Set in an elevated position, this private, detached holiday cottage in Mid Wales enjoys beautiful panoramic views of the surrounding countryside. Its central location provides a great base to explore Mid and North Wales. With a welcoming wood burner and scenic patio seating it is also a great place to relax and do absolutely nothing. Caf&eacute;, village shop and pub within 1 mile.<br />
<br />
<strong>Ground Floor</strong><br />
<br />
The kitchen / dinning area is a light and airy open plan room. Kitchen includes a small breakfast bar, electric double oven, gas hob, microwave and fridge. Dining table for 5 in front of scenic patio doors. These beautiful views over farm land towards rolling hills can also be enjoyed through the kitchen window.<br />
<br />
Cosy lounge includes seating for 5 in front of a welcoming wood burning stove, TV and DVD player. Double patio doors with side lights giving access to the front garden. Distant views of hills from patio doors.<br />
<br />
Large, spacious utility room with freezer, inset sink in worktop and plenty of shelves and cupboards for luggage. Large capacity washing machine and a tumble dryer included. Adjoining cloakroom with coat pegs, shoe rack and separate W.C.<br />
<br />
Bedroom 1 &ndash; Double bedroom with walk in wardrobe, bedside tables with lamps and a chair. Lovely views over the front garden towards rolling hills.<br />
<br />
Bedroom 2 &ndash; Twin bedroom with wardrobe, bedside table with lamp and distant views of hills to the rear.<br />
<br />
Bedroom 3 &ndash; Spacious single bedroom with wardrobe, chest of drawers, chair and the same beautiful view as bedroom 1.<br />
<br />
Bathroom includes a bath and a separate shower with handrails, wash hand basin, W.C. and electric heater.<br />
<br />
<strong>Garden</strong><br />
<br />
Two private patios with wonderful countryside views &ndash; one at the front (with a covered bench and kissing seat) and one at the rear. Front patio leads to a private garden with a garden bench to enjoy the panoramic views.<br />
<br />
<strong>Additional Information</strong>
<ul>
	<li>Bed linen, hand and bath towels provided.</li>
	<li>Central heating and electricity included.</li>
	<li>Complimentary basket of logs for the wood burner. &pound;4 per basket if more is requested</li>
	<li>Wi-fi provided</li>
	<li>Loop for hard of hearing available at the cottage</li>
	<li>1 pet allowed upon request.</li>
	<li>&pound;70 (security refundable bond) payable on arrival or via pre-auth from payment card.</li>
	<li>No smoking</li>
	<li>Plenty of private parking spaces</li>
	<li>Bikes available on request</li>
</ul>

